o.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n某啲情況可能犯法，例如聲明永久離開香港可以提早攞強積金，如果之後被發現唔係永久離開香港就犯法。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mpfa.org.hk/tch/information_centre/forms/mpf_schemes/scheme_members/payment_of_accrued_benefits/files/Annex_D_to_IV_4_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfa.org.hk%2Ftch%2Finformation_centre%2Fforms%2Fmpf_schemes%2Fscheme_members%2Fpayment_of_accrued_benefits%2Ffiles%2FAnnex_D_to_IV_4_c.pdf&d=RPK1G0yWOc9aoPi5Txb6ZqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=c3dc797e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mpfa.org.hk/tch/information_centre/forms/mpf_schemes/scheme_members/payment_of_accrued_benefits/files/Annex_D_to_IV_4_c.pdf</a></blockquote><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n其實呢種情況係咪政府會check你出入境紀錄？純粹問下 我唔係呢個情況</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n非法律撚，在政府做緊<br />\n<br />\n通常政府有私隱政策<br />\n唔會咁容易將內部的data比其他政府部門做野<br />\n詳細你睇返入境處的私隱政策"},{"pid":"c19ee734c92f2e9a776a707cc6faf2aa03930fb5","tid":467618,"uid":112321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:26:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果我同人簽左一份聲明係講話: 我係2年之內都唔會返回香港。<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪係2年內有急事都唔可以翻黎香港？翻左就姐係犯法？<br />\n<br />\nthanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n某啲情況可能犯法，例如聲明永久離開香港可以提早攞強積金，如果之後被發現唔係永久離開香港就犯法。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mpfa.org.hk/tch/information_centre/forms/mpf_schemes/scheme_members/payment_of_accrued_benefits/files/Annex_D_to_IV_4_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfa.org.hk%2Ftch%2Finformation_centre%2Fforms%2Fmpf_schemes%2Fscheme_members%2Fpayment_of_accrued_benefits%2Ffiles%2FAnnex_D_to_IV_4_c.pdf&d=RPK1G0yWOc9aoPi5Txb6ZqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=c3dc797e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mpfa.org.hk/tch/information_centre/forms/mpf_schemes/scheme_members/payment_of_accrued_benefits/files/Annex_D_to_IV_4_c.pdf</a></blockquote><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n其實呢種情況係咪政府會check你出入境紀錄？純粹問下 我唔係呢個情況</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n非法律撚，在政府做緊<br />\n<br />\n通常政府有私隱政策<br />\n唔會咁容易將內部的data比其他政府部門做野<br />\n詳細你睇返入境處的私隱政策</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁其實上面個情況 政府可以點監管？"},{"pid":"9552eb59280fade3963fef61d4b7c02f50cb154b","tid":467618,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:08:13.000Z","msg":"中英聯合聲明夠話香港五十年不變啦 咁你話喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152a37ae75221ff36c42fc9dac845697b546865f","tid":467618,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T15:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果我同人簽左一份聲明係講話: 我係2年之內都唔會返回香港。<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪係2年內有急事都唔可以翻黎香港？翻左就姐係犯法？<br />\n<br />\nthanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n某啲情況可能犯法，例如聲明永久離開香港可以提早攞強積金，如果之後被發現唔係永久離開香港就犯法。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mpfa.org.hk/tch/information_centre/forms/mpf_schemes/scheme_members/payment_of_accrued_benefits/files/Annex_D_to_IV_4_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfa.org.hk%2Ftch%2Finformation_centre%2Fforms%2Fmpf_schemes%2Fscheme_members%2Fpayment_of_accrued_benefits%2Ffiles%2FAnnex_D_to_IV_4_c.pdf&d=RPK1G0yWOc9aoPi5Txb6ZqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=c3dc797e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mpfa.org.hk/tch/information_centre/forms/mpf_schemes/scheme_members/payment_of_accrued_benefits/files/Annex_D_to_IV_4_c.pdf</a></blockquote><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n其實呢種情況係咪政府會check你出入境紀錄？純粹問下 我唔係呢個情況</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n非法律撚，在政府做緊<br />\n<br />\n通常政府有私隱政策<br />\n唔會咁容易將內部的data比其他政府部門做野<br />\n詳細你睇返入境處的私隱政策</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁其實上面個情況 政府可以點監管？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇返policy先知<br />\n內部data都要有access right先入得<br />\n唔會俾非有關負責的同事和部門睇到"}]}